      "level": "H2",
      "text": "Overview",
      "page": 1
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "This sample consists of a simple form containing four distinct fields. The data file contains eight",
      "page": 1
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "separate records.",
      "page": 1
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "By default, the data file will produce a PDF file containing eight separate pages. The selective",
      "page": 1
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "use of the bookmark file will produce the same PDF with a separate pane containing",
      "page": 1
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "bookmarks. This screenshot of the sample output shows a PDF file with bookmarks.",
      "page": 1
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "The left pane displays the available bookmarks for this PDF. You may need to enable the",
      "page": 1
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "display of bookmarks in Adobe\uf8e8 Acrobat\uf8e8 Reader by clicking Window > Show Bookmarks.",
      "page": 1
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Selecting a date from the left pane displays the corresponding page within the document.",
      "page": 1
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Note that the index has been sorted according to the specification in the bookmark file, and that",
      "page": 1
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "pages within the file are created according to the original order in the data file.",
      "page": 1
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Sample Bookmark File",
      "page": 2
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Sample Data File",
      "page": 2
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "The example bookmark file includes three distinct sections:",
      "page": 2
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Invoices sorted, ascending, by date.",
      "page": 2
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Invoices sorted, ascending, by item type.",
      "page": 2
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Invoices sorted, descending, by transaction amount.",
      "page": 2
    },
