      "level": "H2",
      "text": "Deploying the Sample",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "To deploy this sample in your environment:",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "1.  Open the template design ap_bookmark.IFD in Output Designer and recompile the",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "template for the appropriate presentment target.",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "2.  Modify the -z option in the ^job command in the data file ap_bookmark.dat to:",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "\u2022",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "\u2022",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "\u2022",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Identify the target output device.",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Identify the bookmark file using the -abmk command.",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Identify the section for which to generate bookmarks, if desired, using the -abms",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "command.",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "For example,",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "To bookmark by (cid:133)",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Use the command line parameter (cid:133)",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Invoices",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Type",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Amount",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "3.  Place the accompanying files in directories consistent with your implementation:",
      "page": 4
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "\u2022  Place ap_bookmark.IFD in the Designs subdirectory for Output Designer.",
      "page": 4
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "\u2022  Place ap_bookmark.mdf in the forms subdirectory accessible to Central.",
      "page": 4
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "\u2022  Place ap_bookmark.bmk in an addressable directory.",
      "page": 4
    },
